      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――すずの誕生祭当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of Suzu's birthday festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 166.6666667,
          "startTime": 0.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.2999998887
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.9666664679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "二代目星降る奇跡、成宮すずの誕生祭\nみなさん、楽しんでいらっしゃいますかー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The second “Starry Miracle”‚ Suzu Narumiya's Birthday Festival!\nIs everyone having a good time~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5999997775,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2200.0000079,
          "startTime": 11.7999997854
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.1455544153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "星見市が生んだプリンセス、すずにゃん様と\nみんなでもっともっと盛り上がっていこー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s get even more hyped up with\nHoshimi City's princess‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6666654903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.2156920115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は……とってもおめでたい日……\n国民の祝日になっても、おかしくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today… is a very auspicious day…\nIt wouldn’t be strange if it were a national holiday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9000004767,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10999.999308699998,
          "startTime": 37.8999997854
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.9222676594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、ええ！　その通りですわ！\n今日この日を、成宮すず誕生記念日といたします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes! You're right!\nI hereby declare today as Suzu Narumiya's birthday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4522680282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一ヶ月前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― One month ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1318358738,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1653.7647246999968,
          "startTime": 42.7856005985
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 42.3318358737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "やりましたわ、やりましたわ～！\nこれから忙しくなりますわよ～！　ふふふ～ん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did it‚ I did it~!\nI'm going to be busy from now on! Hahaha",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4189318973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、すずにゃん、嬉しいことでもあった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Suzu-nyan‚ did something good happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9088861145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、そうですわね\n嬉しいことって言えば、嬉しいことでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah.\nI guess it is a good thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6117235023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか……そわそわ、してる……？\nいつも以上に、落ち着きがない……かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem… restless…?\nYou're even more… restless than usual…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1333315211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことありませんわ！\n私はいつだって落ち着いてますわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ I’m not!\nI’m always calm!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6345753192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……すずちゃんに、何かあったことは、間違いない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Something definitely happened to Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6522140817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "二人がどうしても気になるなら\n教えてあげないこともないですけど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if you two are that curious‚\nI guess I could tell you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.958928569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、別にいいかな。無理に聞くのも悪いし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ it’s fine. I don’t want to force you to tell us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0891068931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！？　待ってくださいまし！\n聞いて損する話ではありませんわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? Hold on!\nYou won’t regret hearing it!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.908466355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、ごめんごめん。最初から聞くつもりだったよ\nすずにゃん、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ sorry‚ sorry. I was going to listen from the start.\nSo Suzu-nyan‚ what’s up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9666516303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "では教えて差し上げます。なんと今回、私に『ミラ\nクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の話が来ましたの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ let me tell you. Surprisingly‚\nI was offered a spot on “Miracle☆Idol Birthday!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2882212161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "それって、アイドルのやりたかったことを叶えてくれる\n雑誌のお誕生日企画……だよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s that birthday project in the magazine\nwhere they grant idols their wishes… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣がこの前やったやつだー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the one Mei did a while back~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4998575366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ！　そしてこちらの企画にて、私の誕生日記念\nイベントを開催することに決まりましたわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep! And they’ve decided to hold a birthday event\nfor me for this project!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3526995183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "題して……『祝・成宮家の令嬢、二代目星降る奇跡\n時代のニューウェーブ、成宮すずの生誕祭』！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The title is… “Celebrating the Lady of the Narumiya Family‚ the Second ‘Starry Miracle‚’\nthe New Wave of the Era‚ Suzu Narumiya's Birthday Festival!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.5527076563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おお～っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.629828723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "……って、何するの？\n誕生日パーティーだから、みんなでケーキ食べたり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What’s it about?\nSince it’s a birthday party‚ are we all gonna eat cake?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.0666790963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "それは普通のパーティーですわ！\n私の生誕祭ですもの、目玉はソロライブステージ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a normal party!\nMy birthday festival should have a solo live as the main event――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0769298715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "それからファンのみなさんとクイズ大会も……\nあっ！　記念写真を撮るのもいいですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then a quiz competition with all the fans…\nAh! Taking commemorative photos would be great too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.0102642221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日イベント、凄く熱い……！\nファンにとって、最も特別な日……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A birthday event‚ that's awesome…!\nThe most special day for the fans…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.2666801136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "雫がこの反応ならば、ファンのみなさんも\n待ち望んでいたはずでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Shizuku’s reacting like this‚ then the fans\nmust be looking forward to it as well!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.8830079558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、私の生誕祭には大勢の人が来ますわね\nドームクラスの会場じゃないと収まりませんわ",
